The <a href="/en-US/docs/Web/API/KeyboardEvent" title="KeyboardEvent objects describe a user interaction with the keyboard; each event describes a single interaction between the user and a key (or combination of a key with modifier keys) on the keyboard."><code>KeyboardEvent</code></a> interface's <code><strong>key</strong></code> read-only property returns the value of the key pressed by the user, taking into consideration the state of modifier keys such as <kbd>Shift</kbd> as well as the keyboard locale and layout.